text: @UPS @UPSHelp  can you guys train your drivers to look at the house numbers before you drop off packages?? Several time my pigs and my neighbors are showing up at each others house. It’s not that hard to maybe I don’t know slow down and read.

@StevenDAmbrozio I understand your frustration. Drivers should be checking the addresses before leaving packages. Can you please DM me your tracking number along with your phone number? Please also confirm your address vs. the address where the driver is leaving them. ^ML https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ
